// Application Entry Point
// Mounts the React app to #root and wires up all top-level routes for the Collab, Kodex, Onboarding, and Pseudo Viewer sections.
// synced: 2026-03-26T13:51:59Z

Top-level routing via BrowserRouter + Routes. Four route groups:
  /kodex/*      → KodexLayout with nested Dashboard, Topics, TopicDetail, Graph, Drafts, Flags
  /onboarding/* → OnboardingLayout with nested BrowseDashboard, TopicDetail, SearchResults,
                  WelcomeScreen, OnboardingDashboard, TopicGraph, TeamDashboard
  /pseudo/*     → PseudoPage (flat catch-all)
  /*            → App (main Collab catch-all)

